    },
    {
      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "Leave a cleaner path, not a new maze",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Refactoring is maintenance with manners. It helps most when the shape of the change stays obvious.</p>"
        },
